Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.83,KARA-english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:16.38,KARA-japanese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf25}It{\kf8}su{\kf83}ka {\kf18}bo{\kf25}ku {\kf41}ga {\kf36}mis{\kf47}ete {\kf50}a{\kf74}ger{\kf101}u {\kf20}hi{\kf23}kar{\kf26}i {\kf40}no {\kf11}ka{\kf33}gayak{\kf207}u {\kf31}se{\kf25}ka{\kf41}i {\kf14}w{\kf475}o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:16.38,KARA-english,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I'll show you a world that shines in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.02,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(365,343)}Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't be your boyfriend, but I can pretend to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I can't be your boyfriend, but I can pretend to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll try my best to make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll try my best to make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show her L's face and find out his name, then I'll erase him along with his investigation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing her can wait till after...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one person that knows Kira's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave her alive for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pretend to be", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get to the point: will you show Misa your Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to if I want her to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... {\alpha&HFF&}turn around for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... turn around for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Even though you're a Shinigami, you and Rem are completely different types!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you, if only by name, Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Light! Do you know how Shinigami die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already using Light, my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can I call you "Knight" instead of "Light", then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Misa, you're like a knight on a white horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Light" is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seriously going to check all the video footage from Aoyama on the 22nd all by yourself, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}There is a real possibility that Kira and the second Kira made contact there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There is a real possibility that Kira and the second Kira made contact there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to check all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Yagami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have Mogi-san keep a close eye on Light-kun's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light's movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by any chance he really is Kira, the second Kira may try to approach him in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when Ryuuzaki actually sleeps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught him sleeping, just like that, in his chair once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that if a Shinigami has feelings for a specific human, {\alpha&HFF&}and kills another human, in order to prolong the lifespan of the one they have feelings for... they'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that if a Shinigami has feelings for a specific human, and kills another human, in order to prolong the lifespan of the one they have feelings for... {\alpha&HFF&}they'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that if a Shinigami has feelings for a specific human, and kills another human, in order to prolong the lifespan of the one they have feelings for... they'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine that any Shinigami would do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll certainly never do anything of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where have you been sending the video tapes to the TV station from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... {\alpha&HFF&}the first one was from Osaka, then from Tokyo, and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the first one was from Osaka, {\alpha&HFF&}then from Tokyo, and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the first one was from Osaka, then from Tokyo, {\alpha&HFF&}and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the first one was from Osaka, then from Tokyo, and the last one was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to ensure that they couldn't pin down an exact location, so I used the shinkansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:13.98,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinkansen is a network of high-speed railway lines in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}you still have tapes and envelopes with your friend's fingerprints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you still have tapes and envelopes with your friend's fingerprints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better destroy everything you used to make those videos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, after we send the final tape from yet another different location tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have decided not to reveal myself to Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}To the police, thank you very much for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have decided not to reveal myself to Kira. To the police, thank you very much for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, {\alpha&HFF&}and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will begin by passing judgment on all criminals that Kira has not judged already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, {\alpha&HFF&}I shall proceed by sharing these powers with people that I find worthy and would like to continue making this world a better place."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall proceed by sharing these powers with people that I find worthy and would like to continue making this world a better place."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Share these powers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply a line to confuse the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there are already two people who have this power, {\alpha&HFF&}it's not inconceivable that there may be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there are already two people who have this power, it's not inconceivable that there may be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they believe that this figure could increase, they'll become more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "Can you do this?". Just tell me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do whatever you ask of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more important thing that I've got to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught by the police... {\alpha&HFF&}even if we get caught as suspects... we can't mention anything about each other or the notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught by the police... even if we get caught as suspects... {\alpha&HFF&}we can't mention anything about each other or the notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught by the police... even if we get caught as suspects... we can't mention anything about each other or the notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless they have the notebooks, there is no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you swear to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this concludes the boyfriend-girlfriend contract, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, now for my stipulations:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At minimum, there must be at least one date a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't get it after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you won't understand unless I spell it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L already suspects that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this "L" is really impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people believes that he knows nothing, or that he's an idiot, when in fact he's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it's entirely thanks to that, {\alpha&HFF&}but I've managed to get in direct contact with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it's entirely thanks to that, but I've managed to get in direct contact with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L and Kira are in contact?! {\alpha&HFF&}Both of you are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L and Kira are in contact?! Both of you are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a little excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L thinks that even if I am Kira, as long as he keeps his name hidden, he's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, to investigate me further, he revealed himself to me as "L".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the only proof he has, is that he has no other suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if I act naturally around him, {\alpha&HFF&}I expect he'll trust me and we'll investigate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if I act naturally around him, I expect he'll trust me and we'll investigate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, all you have to do is take Misa to L?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard enough for me to try and get close to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, {\alpha&HFF&}if someone suddenly starts to make contact with me, while at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, if someone suddenly starts to make contact with me, while at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira and the second Kira's attitudes towards society are changing, {\alpha&HFF&}that person will be suspected of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira and the second Kira's attitudes towards society are changing, that person will be suspected of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspicions of me being Kira will then deepen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow them to think that we've suddenly met and started to go out with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of... is that why you're saying we won't be able to go out on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see me because it'd make them suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}it'd probably be better if you start thinking carefully about how you're going to see L's face without him discovering your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it'd probably be better if you start thinking carefully about how you're going to see L's face without him discovering your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get rid of L, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as possible, I'd like to meet you in person to pass on information...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, {\alpha&HFF&}to ensure that our meetings remain unnoticed, I'll aim to go out with lots of different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, to ensure that our meetings remain unnoticed, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll aim to go out with lots of different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, to ensure that our meetings remain unnoticed, I'll aim to go out with lots of different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be dating other girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it'll come down to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you doing that... I'll kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "chan" now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to change the world, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but... {\alpha&HFF&}Misa loves you more than the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but... Misa loves you more than the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings for me should be those of a supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this is the first time you've ever spoken to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never fallen in love at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I wanted to meet Kira out of gratitude and sympathy, as opposed to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Light, from the first time I saw you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular as ever I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}if you love me, you can obey me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you love me, you can obey me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you said that you didn't mind if I used you, and that you'd do as I say, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't forgive you if I see you with another girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are two completely different issues!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, both Death Notes are in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't obey me, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that... {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that... Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill this girl, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll write your name in my own Death Note... and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill this girl, I'll write your name in my own Death Note... {\alpha&HFF&}and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill this girl, I'll write your name in my own Death Note... and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see this girl's lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she dies before her time, I'll assume that you were responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use the Death Note to kill me, in order to save her, wouldn't you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If you do that, Rem, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct... {\alpha&HFF&}but that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct... but that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Shinigami... {\alpha&HFF&}is she serious? Then from this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Shinigami... is she serious? {\alpha&HFF&}Then from this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Shinigami... is she serious? Then from this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already 11:30. You shouldn't have a girl here so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's true. {\alpha&HFF&}We were busy talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's true. We were busy talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for intruding on you all till such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you should walk her to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, walking around outside with her would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! {\alpha&HFF&}Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. I wasn't too sure about her at first, but she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill the girl, she'll kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'll have to remain on Rem's good side until she dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I'll have to protect her from getting caught by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Rem, Light truly is my "knight" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, you can't really kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill a Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}you have to make them use their Death Note to save someone they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill a Shinigami, you have to make them use their Death Note to save someone they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, I can't try to kill her first by manipulating someone via the Death Note to attack Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa gets intro trouble, I'll be the first person she'll suspect, and I'll be killed straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, Rem's an even bigger threat than L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}She's... doing something as high profile as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's... {\alpha&HFF&}doing something as high profile as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's... doing something as high profile as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.06,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa\NReal name: Amane Misa\NHometown: Kyoto\ND.O.B.: 1987 December 25th\NSize: 152 tall, 76 bust, 51 waist, 75 hip\NBlood type: AB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if they find out that I'm seeing someone like her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! No matter how I look at it, she's just getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! More importantly, I need to think of a method of using Misa's eyes to kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could get rid of L...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Sayu, can you not mention Misa-chan to father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not just father either. {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like you not to mention this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not just father either. I'd like you not to mention this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an up-and-coming model, so she's not really supposed to have a boyfriend or anything along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Really?! No wonder I thought she was cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from a girlfriend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep your secret... for 5,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.53,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}Toudou University
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final message from Misa will arrive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be passed directly to the investigation, instead of going to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should stop by Investigative Headquarters and check L's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}you said that you'd go out with me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... you said that you'd go out with me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we are, sitting together in lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you don't seem the least bit happy about it. {\alpha&HFF&}You seem distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you don't seem the least bit happy about it. You seem distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:28.28,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Toudai is similar to a beauty pageant title. Meaning she's one of the prettiest girls around Toudou University.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that going out with "Miss Toudai" means that many people will be saying things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And truthfully, you are extremely beautiful, Takada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't dwell upon such matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like fickle things such as "Miss Whatever".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she clearly didn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go at our own pace without worrying about others, okay, Takada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, you've arrived at a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just received another video from the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They state that this is the final one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.26,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided not to reveal myself to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:18.67,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,To the police, thank you very much for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:26.26,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will join Kira in purging the world of evil, and will gain their acceptance through aiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:30.01,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will begin by passing judgment on all criminals that Kira has not judged already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:37.03,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall proceed by sharing these powers with people that I find worthy and would like to continue making this world a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having watched this, {\alpha&HFF&}I get the feeling that Kira and the second Kira have made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having watched this, I get the feeling that Kira and the second Kira have made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you feel that they've made contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed that you would get the same impression as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:15:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fact that their insistence on meeting Kira has completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the fact that they now want to judge all the criminals Kira hasn't yet judged in order to be accepted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why hadn't they done that from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they hadn't thought so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presumably, they've managed to make contact with Kira, who told them to pass this judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has also asked to conceal this link between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Kira is acting without thinking too much then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened to stop them from thinking so clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they're trying to confuse me by making the connection between them obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically, this connection is a huge threat... {\alpha&HFF&}but due to this, my suspicions towards Light-kun have lessened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically, this connection is a huge threat... but due to this, {\alpha&HFF&}my suspicions towards Light-kun have lessened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically, this connection is a huge threat... but due to this, my suspicions towards Light-kun have lessened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light-kun was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}instead of sending a tape like this, I believe that he'd get the second Kira to make another threat forcing L... that is, me, to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light-kun was Kira, instead of sending a tape like this, {\alpha&HFF&}I believe that he'd get the second Kira to make another threat forcing L... that is, me, to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light-kun was Kira, instead of sending a tape like this, I believe that he'd get the second Kira to make another threat forcing L... that is, me, to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we assumed they hadn't made contact yet, {\alpha&HFF&}it would be the second Kira's responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we assumed they hadn't made contact yet, it would be the second Kira's responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all he'd need to get them to say is:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. {\alpha&HFF&}But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. Kira should be pleased if L dies. There's no way that they would try and stop me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira should be pleased if L dies. There's no way that they would try and stop me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. Kira should be pleased if L dies. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way that they would try and stop me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I stopped once when Kira told me to. But I no longer believe that that warning came from Kira. Kira should be pleased if L dies. There's no way that they would try and stop me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I truly were Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I truly were Kira... I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you genuinely are L, then I know your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you're threatened, there's no way that you'd actually appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would never consider taking the fall for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, you'd have some sort of plan to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, even if it's purely theoretical, I want you to stop with this "If I were Kira" talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to express my thoughts clearly to Ryuuzaki, so that the case can end quickly, and so that my name can be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the reason I can say "If I were Kira", is because I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct... {\alpha&HFF&}Light-kun isn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct... Light-kun isn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, {\alpha&HFF&}it'd be a problem if he was, because... Light-kun is... the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it'd be a problem if he was, because... {\alpha&HFF&}Light-kun is... the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it'd be a problem if he was, because... Light-kun is... {\alpha&HFF&}the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it'd be a problem if he was, because... Light-kun is... the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend that I really get along with as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lonely with you being absent from university.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to play tennis with you again at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friend"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friend", huh? Well, good for you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... he's easily managed to deduce the connection between Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll need to get rid of my enemies as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even more dangerous to meet Misa from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait an entire two weeks, so I was just on my way over to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time in my entire life that I seriously wanted to hit a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just really wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd better come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl... again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen a lot of magazines with you in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, can we have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Misa's ally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, {\alpha&HFF&}I've seen this girl a number of times from the Shinigami world, and due to certain circumstances, I've got some feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I've seen this girl a number of times from the Shinigami world, and due to certain circumstances, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got some feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I've seen this girl a number of times from the Shinigami world, and due to certain circumstances, I've got some feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got feelings, despite being a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you don't like the fact that I said, "If you kill this girl, I'll kill you".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does this mean that if Misa is happy, you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see her sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa really... {\alpha&HFF&}likes me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa really... likes me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my happiness your happiness too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you ask Rem to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy, {\alpha&HFF&}yet if one of us is caught by L, that happiness will be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy, yet if one of us is caught by L, {\alpha&HFF&}that happiness will be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy, yet if one of us is caught by L, that happiness will be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Shinigami aren't supposed to tell humans other people's names, {\alpha&HFF&}there's no rule that stipulates who Rem can and can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Shinigami aren't supposed to tell humans other people's names, there's no rule that stipulates who Rem can and can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll have even greater feelings for Misa, and I'd be thankful to you too, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L, I'll have even greater feelings for Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}and I'd be thankful to you too, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L, I'll have even greater feelings for Misa, and I'd be thankful to you too, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we'd both be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I want to be loved by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us will be happy... I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, {\alpha&HFF&}so even if I end up prolonging your life, it won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, so even if I end up prolonging your life, it won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L. {\alpha&HFF&}He means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L. He means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, Rem! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... {\alpha&HFF&}just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... just like that?
